<subSubSection pageId="178" pageNumber="456" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="178.[169,1379,2223,2887]" pageId="178" pageNumber="456">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[175,532,2775,2808]" pageId="178" pageNumber="456">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not assessed on The IUCN Red List as a separate species from the Dusky Rice Rat (
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Tomes" baseAuthorityYear="1860" box="[540,734,2814,2847]" class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Melanomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="178" pageNumber="456" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="caliginosus">M. caliginosus</taxonomicName>
), which is classified as Least Concern.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
